name: Simleader
overview: “The limitless” is a concept which has entered into our life and became a synonym of free dialogue. Company “СимЛидер” sells wholesale and retail limitless tariffs and direct numbers since 2004, we dealers on these cards of such communications service providers as MTS, a Biline and the Megaphone. “SimLeader.Ru” constantly improves tariffs, quality of service and a cooperation condition, offering clients only the best goods and services which exist in the mobile communication market. Our clients are physical and legal bodies who regard as of paramount importance possibility always to be on communication, after all with our help communication really became accessible. Getting a limitless sim card in our company, we will fill your life with dialogue freedom with which help you give more attention to your business and dialogue with friends and relatives. “The limitless” is not the tariff, it is a way of life! We with pleasure perceive criticism, with high enthusiasm we consider interesting offers and are always open for cooperation!
